title: War of the Roses: She Got Pregnant to Make Him Stay
description: Gina's boyfriend has cheated on her before.  She wanted to make things work and thought the only way to do it was to get pregnant.  Now they have a child and he came home with a "rug burn" the other day.  Did Gina's plan to have a child with him work or is he still up to no good?
